{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01GwL5mcWkReBzbxXfEcwTxi","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# codeharness observability stack — OpenSearch/ELK backend\n     2→# Generated by /harness-init with --observability-backend elk.\n     3→# All images use pinned versions (NFR8).\n     4→\n     5→services:\n     6→  opensearch:\n     7→    image: opensearchproject/opensearch:2.17.1\n     8→    container_name: codeharness-opensearch\n     9→    environment:\n    10→      - discovery.type=single-node\n    11→      - DISABLE_SECURITY_PLUGIN=true\n    12→      - OPENSEARCH_JAVA_OPTS=-Xms512m -Xmx512m\n    13→    ports:\n    14→      - \"9200:9200\"\n    15→    volumes:\n    16→      - opensearch-data:/usr/share/opensearch/data\n    17→    networks:\n    18→      - codeharness-net\n    19→    healthcheck:\n    20→      test: [\"CMD\", \"curl\", \"-sf\", \"http://127.0.0.1:9200/_cluster/health\"]\n    21→      interval: 10s\n    22→      timeout: 5s\n    23→      retries: 5\n    24→\n    25→  opensearch-dashboards:\n    26→    image: opensearchproject/opensearch-dashboards:2.17.1\n    27→    container_name: codeharness-dashboards\n    28→    environment:\n    29→      - OPENSEARCH_HOSTS=[\"http://opensearch:9200\"]\n    30→      - DISABLE_SECURITY_DASHBOARDS_PLUGIN=true\n    31→    ports:\n    32→      - \"5601:5601\"\n    33→    depends_on:\n    34→      opensearch:\n    35→        condition: service_healthy\n    36→    networks:\n    37→      - codeharness-net\n    38→\n    39→  otel-collector:\n    40→    image: otel/opentelemetry-collector-contrib:0.114.0\n    41→    container_name: codeharness-otel\n    42→    ports:\n    43→      - \"4317:4317\"   # OTLP gRPC\n    44→      - \"4318:4318\"   # OTLP HTTP\n    45→    volumes:\n    46→      - ./otel-collector-config.yaml:/etc/otelcol-contrib/config.yaml:ro\n    47→    depends_on:\n    48→      opensearch:\n    49→        condition: service_healthy\n    50→    networks:\n    51→      -