{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01GaG8f17e6zyLPxFZQ43muo","type":"tool_result","content":"   233→\n   234→### Change Log\n   235→\n   236→- 2026-03-25: Story created with 10 ACs (3 from epic, 7 derived from architecture analysis, existing code audit, testing, and line-limit enforcement). Full implementation guidance with file locations, line budgets, current-state assessment, and anti-patterns. Status set to ready-for-dev.\n   237→- 2026-03-25: All tasks implemented. Added `--observability-backend` CLI option, `otlp.backend` state field, backend-aware Docker health checks, ELK compose template, and unit tests. Status set to review.\n   238→- 2026-03-25: Code review (adversarial). Fixed 4 issues: (1) HIGH — missing CLI validation for `--observability-backend` allows arbitrary values; (2) MEDIUM — ELK compose file resolution in `formatters.ts` always resolved to Victoria compose for shared stacks; (3) MEDIUM — Victoria-specific endpoints shown for ELK backend; (4) MEDIUM — `resolveEndpoints()` not backend-aware. Added `ELK_ENDPOINTS`, `getDefaultEndpointsForBackend()`, `resolveSharedCompose()`. Added 9 new tests. Status set to verifying.\n   239→\n   240→### File List\n   241→\n   242→- `src/commands/init.ts` — Added `--observability-backend` CLI option (+3 lines)\n   243→- `src/modules/infra/types.ts` — Added `observabilityBackend` to `InitOptions` (+1 line)\n   244→- `src/lib/state.ts` — Added `backend` field to otlp interface, backfill in migrateState (+5 lines)\n   245→- `src/modules/infra/init-project.ts` — Store backend choice, handle 'none' backend early return, backend validation (+28 lines)\n   246→- `src/modules/infra/docker-setup.ts` — Select compose file based on backend (+2 lines)\n   247→- `src/modules/status/formatters.ts` — Backend-aware Docker checks in handleDockerCheck, handleFullStatus, handleHealthCheck, ELK compose resolution fix (+31 lines)\n   248→- `src/modules/status/endpoints.ts` — Added `ELK_ENDPOINTS`, `getDefaultEndpointsForBackend()`, backend-aware `resolveEndpoints()` (+16 lines)\n   249→- `src/lib/stack-path.ts` — Added `getElkComposeFilePath()` (+4 lines)\n   250→- `templates/docker-compose.elk.yml` — New: OpenSearch + Dashboards + OTel Collector compose (58 lines)\n   251→- `src/modules/infra/__tests__/docker-setup.test.ts` — Added backend-aware compose selection tests\n   252→- `src/modules/infra/__tests__/init-project.test.ts` — Added `--observability-backend` option tests + invalid backend validation test\n   253→- `src/modules/status/__tests__/formatters-docker-check.test.ts` — New: backend-aware Docker check tests + ELK compose resolution + ELK endpoints\n   254→- `src/modules/status/__tests__/endpoints.test.ts` — Added ELK endpoints and `getDefaultEndpointsForBackend` tests"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01MwzbgNwEhenGxNXV9UQBeX","session_id":"507a8d0b-20bb-4c55-954f-5f817ca0f972","uuid":"f91a66fc-d14c-43cf-87d1-e82d413797c6","timestamp":"2026-03-27T07:12:55.019Z"}
